Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.83,0:00:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳同学 怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.48,0:00:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没甚么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.88,0:00:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请走这边 祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.19,0:00:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.92,0:00:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳 这个给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.87,0:00:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉安女学园 山百合版灰姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.40,0:00:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经用萤光笔作上了记号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.47,0:00:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉红色的是灰姑娘 蓝色的是姐姐B
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.45,0:00:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐B？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.89,0:00:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是灰姑娘的坏心眼姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.56,0:00:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你不演灰姑娘时 希望你能演这个角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.23,0:00:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.77,0:00:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来你为甚么会在这种地方吃午饭呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.85,0:00:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳同学正在逃避新闻部的采访呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.52,0:01:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 我们学校的新闻部采访的方法很强硬啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.34,0:01:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳 接受念珠吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.48,0:01:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就可以替你回答那些采访
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.29,0:01:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.38,0:01:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿意的话 可以随时来找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.03,0:01:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.04,0:01:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还本想让她同意在校庆时展示照片呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.50,0:01:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 祥子大人讨厌樱花与银杏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.05,0:01:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.82,0:01:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才让人吃惊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.98,0:01:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.74,0:01:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她竟然能坚持着到这里来找佑巳同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.95,0:01:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.31,0:01:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集在玛莉亚的庭院里的少女们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.90,0:01:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也带着天使般无垢的笑容 穿越与身同高的门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.28,0:02:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覆盖住纯洁身心的是深色的制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.88,0:02:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让裙子的摺痕乱掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.76,0:02:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让白色的水手服领结外翻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.91,0:02:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒缓地行走成了这里的习俗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.94,0:02:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私立莉莉安女学园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.38,0:02:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是少女的花园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.28,0:03:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)}月与念珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.80,0:04:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.68,0:04:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.87,0:04:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能请教一个问题吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.12,0:04:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困难的问题可别找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.98,0:04:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为甚么白蔷薇大人会选志摩子同学做妹妹呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.46,0:04:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.81,0:04:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是很困难不过倒是很少见的问题啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.31,0:04:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于选择志摩子的原因一般不会有谁问到呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.19,0:04:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是因为志摩子同学\n看起来就像是应该被选中的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.90,0:04:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我完全相反
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.01,0:04:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得这么软弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.80,0:04:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 我是稻秸嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.55,0:04:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是甚么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.38,0:04:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是白蔷薇大人说的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.70,0:04:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对祥子大人来说 我是迎头撞上并被抓住的稻秸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.75,0:04:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这样说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.23,0:04:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我还真佩服自己能比喻得这么好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.57,0:04:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稻秸 不是很好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.58,0:04:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一点好呀？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.19,0:04:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是被祥子一直握在手里这一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.42,0:05:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像志摩子这种人材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.57,0:05:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得就该让她为山百合会好好发挥其才能吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.02,0:05:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是刚才的问题的答案吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.57,0:05:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以白蔷薇的身份回答的话 这个就是答案了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.13,0:05:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 以个人来说到还有其它的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.73,0:05:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.76,0:05:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我的看法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.57,0:05:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否反倒是志摩子在羡慕着佑巳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.76,0:05:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了 为甚么会突然跳到那种话上啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.43,0:05:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.90,0:05:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看看佑巳那可爱而又变化丰富的表情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.47,0:05:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等… 白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.05,0:05:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然“长者”来了就到此结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.91,0:05:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长者？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.03,0:05:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来好像很开心嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.65,0:05:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦 就是看见祥子进来才服务一下的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.85,0:05:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.57,0:06:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 不快点洗杯子的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.96,0:06:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是大家快到这里的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.63,0:06:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳真是一个好孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.80,0:06:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让祥子嫉妒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.91,0:06:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我也该去看看楼下的情形了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.43,0:06:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会穿上红色的天鹅绒礼服去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.94,0:06:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我穿着平常的裙子就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.20,0:06:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我要在有金色花卉图案的披风上别上钻石别针
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.28,0:06:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 头发像这样如何呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.24,0:06:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙杜瑞拉 你跟我们一起去舞会不是挺好的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.54,0:06:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是记得很好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.70,0:07:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使被白蔷薇大人抚摸头或拥抱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.67,0:07:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也从未有过这么强烈的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.19,0:07:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 刚才去取剧装了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 好像真的是正在忙碌中呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.56,0:07:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在做剧本的练习而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.25,0:07:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要试穿服装吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.60,0:07:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.84,0:07:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为今天是试穿服装与排练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.31,0:07:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以花寺的学生会长也会过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.46,0:07:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经清楚地转告过了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.29,0:07:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子也需要参加的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也该是去迎接的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.46,0:07:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳 你能去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.61,0:07:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柏木同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.13,0:07:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 也就是花寺的学生会长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.70,0:07:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该在正门那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.22,0:07:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.00,0:07:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能跑 不能跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.66,0:07:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还会踩到银杏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.48,0:07:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 失礼了 请问是柏木同学吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.17,0:08:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是山百合会的人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.14,0:08:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是柏木优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.12,0:08:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天请多多关照了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.15,0:08:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经确定能进入花寺的大学了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.37,0:08:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是附属中学 若非成绩优秀是不可能不参加考试就合格吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.20,0:08:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.19,0:08:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 能否在这里稍等片刻呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.29,0:08:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去换一下拖鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.90,0:08:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是让人无法挑剔的王子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.36,0:08:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却被灰姑娘所讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.76,0:08:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.95,0:08:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我看错了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.82,0:08:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人应该在蔷薇馆里才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.21,0:08:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢各位的款待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.01,0:08:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常漂亮的公馆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.79,0:08:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人不在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.50,0:08:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.34,0:08:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.62,0:08:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花寺的学生会长 客观地来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.99,0:09:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.27,0:09:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客观来看 相当的不错啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.52,0:09:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说作为祥子的对手没甚么不足的地方了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.33,0:09:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.24,0:09:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的戏剧其实还有另一个目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.61,0:09:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是克服祥子的厌男症
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.23,0:09:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子的家庭相当地复杂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.46,0:09:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖父与父亲都在外面偷藏了女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.67,0:09:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人会讨厌男人原来也是事出有由啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.79,0:09:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 灰姑娘呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.25,0:09:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了句“我先去体育馆”就走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.65,0:09:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.50,0:09:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我也先去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.82,0:09:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才看见的果然是祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.47,0:09:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说已经回去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.84,0:09:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.65,0:10:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您没回去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.46,0:10:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为甚么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.39,0:10:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才在图书馆旁边的路上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.08,0:10:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没去过那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.21,0:10:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.64,0:10:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裙子会被弄脏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.61,0:10:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么祥子大人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.59,0:10:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才刚注意到这一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.76,0:10:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.14,0:10:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.29,0:10:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其实去过那个地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.67,0:10:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想早点看看对方的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.82,0:10:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有这样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.99,0:11:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想比对方更早地看到 就只有这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.42,0:11:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.53,0:11:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与花寺的学生会长跳舞的确非我本意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.17,0:11:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但逃避就意味着认输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.75,0:11:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起其它任何东西 我最讨厌的就是认输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.48,0:11:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大家到来之前 让我来做你的舞伴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.91,0:11:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不用了 不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.08,0:11:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.78,0:11:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来是记住了舞步 但还无法跳得很流畅吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.14,0:11:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.13,0:11:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算您这样说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.68,0:11:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用想太多 信任自已身体的记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.75,0:11:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别急躁 面带微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.19,0:11:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.58,0:11:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.97,0:11:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.42,0:11:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.82,0:11:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.18,0:11:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.27,0:11:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 舞姿慢慢变得漂亮起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.39,0:11:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳舞原来是一件这么愉快的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.87,0:11:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢 我以前也不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.04,0:12:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 我叫小笠原 请多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.49,0:12:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.09,0:12:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也请你多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.26,0:12:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很帅气吧 柏木同学的王子装扮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.12,0:12:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你们也换装吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.27,0:12:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 佑巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.49,0:12:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.89,0:12:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.23,0:12:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口好像太松了一点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.50,0:12:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要稍微提供一点服务嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.82,0:12:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是甚么服务啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.43,0:12:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将你最美丽的装扮做为礼物送给FAN们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.18,0:12:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 佑巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.04,0:12:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这样最合适吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.71,0:12:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.30,0:12:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.28,0:12:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.73,0:12:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会是你来穿哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.15,0:12:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.42,0:12:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对佑巳来说好像稍微大了点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.45,0:12:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许改小一点会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.96,0:12:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.28,0:13:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会演灰姑娘现在还没决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.54,0:13:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 交换
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.89,0:13:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～ 佑巳也好可爱 好可爱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.79,0:13:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.60,0:13:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 对我来说胸口实在是太松了一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.82,0:13:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.36,0:13:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.75,0:13:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.42,0:13:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.96,0:13:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2 2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.47,0:13:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2 2 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.16,0:13:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.72,0:13:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.28,0:13:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.94,0:13:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.44,0:13:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2 2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.99,0:13:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2 2 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.59,0:13:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.22,0:13:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.54,0:13:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.22,0:13:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.70,0:13:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2 2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.30,0:13:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2 2 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.91,0:13:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.52,0:13:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.95,0:13:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.63,0:13:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.44,0:13:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2 2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.13,0:13:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2 2 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.48,0:13:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 休息15分钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.05,0:13:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子 我知道你不喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.23,0:13:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过能否稍微让大家看见一点笑容？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.22,0:13:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那样会影响到观众的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.44,0:13:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式上场时我会好好地笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.89,0:14:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 如果有我能帮上忙的事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.30,0:14:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就接受我的念珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.64,0:14:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.40,0:14:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说有想拜托佑巳的事 就只有这件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.58,0:14:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真那么讨厌吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.44,0:14:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常讨厌！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.25,0:14:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.58,0:14:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话想对你说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.57,0:14:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳 你先回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.52,0:14:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.37,0:14:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.79,0:14:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.61,0:14:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.84,0:14:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 柏木同学说有话要对她讲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.99,0:14:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位主角都不在 也排练不起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.55,0:14:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 稍等一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.19,0:14:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有回来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.69,0:14:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想就这样放弃排练吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.03,0:14:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子不是那样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.79,0:14:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.26,0:14:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.24,0:15:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我 我也去找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.57,0:15:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分头去找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.73,0:15:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.23,0:15:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蔷薇大人 这种时候了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.34,0:15:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢祥子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.19,0:15:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.87,0:15:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜欢祥子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.73,0:15:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红蔷薇大人与黄蔷薇大人以及令也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.97,0:15:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概志摩子与由乃也是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.46,0:15:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使看起来很干练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.73,0:15:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也衹不过是高中生 所以难免会胆怯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.02,0:15:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕去知道发生了甚么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.47,0:15:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有不该去找出真相的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.71,0:15:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去找祥子大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.01,0:15:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讨厌的银杏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.52,0:15:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.85,0:15:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.46,0:15:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为那家伙绝对不会对祥子出手呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.82,0:15:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为同类所以知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.65,0:16:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干甚么！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.45,0:16:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开你的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.72,0:16:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子 不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.45,0:16:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳 去叫守卫来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.07,0:16:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.72,0:16:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.88,0:16:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为会让祥子大人感到为难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.23,0:16:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为甚么你会这么想？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.18,0:16:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为您脸上这样写着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.19,0:16:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.13,0:16:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惊扰到大家真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.53,0:16:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才只是有点小的争吵而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.40,0:16:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你一定要向大家说明情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.96,0:16:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.86,0:16:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柏木优是我的表兄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.30,0:16:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只如此 他还是我的未婚夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.67,0:16:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未…婚！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.29,0:16:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们即使不作戏也能互拥双肩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.73,0:16:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是接吻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.35,0:17:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得意忘形了吗 还不停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.66,0:17:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.12,0:17:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.31,0:17:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.81,0:17:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我也不知该怎样才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.75,0:17:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我甚么也帮不上祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.83,0:17:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是叫大家来这里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.79,0:17:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.13,0:17:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.71,0:17:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.73,0:18:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.48,0:18:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人 请给我念珠吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.14,0:18:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.42,0:18:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.98,0:18:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.60,0:18:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我改变主意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.44,0:18:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优…他并不喜欢我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.68,0:18:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但因为我是独生女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.23,0:18:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他有带领小笠原集团的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.46,0:18:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双亲都希望我们两人结婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.08,0:18:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他才会说要和我结婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.02,0:18:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.88,0:18:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很喜欢柏木同学吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.69,0:18:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自已喜欢的人并非因为喜欢自已而要与自已结婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.21,0:18:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.17,0:18:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你听我诉说这些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.33,0:18:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也包括我的忏悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.18,0:18:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没法向任何人诉说 所以一直很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.25,0:18:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经不要紧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.22,0:19:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 祥子大人 请给我念珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.65,0:19:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我去战斗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.38,0:19:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再逃避了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.48,0:19:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.35,0:19:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个温室里半数以上的植物都是蔷薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.51,0:19:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是红蔷薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.54,0:19:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四季常开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.32,0:19:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好记住这种花吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.03,0:19:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.98,0:19:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
